20:36.501 --> 20:39.237
¶ You worry too much ¶
(panting)

20:39.239 --> 20:41.939
(panting continues)

20:41.941 --> 20:45.343
¶ All those sunny days ¶

20:45.345 --> 20:48.012
(grunts)
- Yeah! (laughs)

